title: The Contenders (Round 1)
itunes:title: The Contenders (Round 1)
description: Every year since 1992 Two Guys Smoke Shop has been announcing The Cigar of the Year. But it all starts with "The Contenders;" 7 of the hottest and best cigars in the industry, and on today's Cigar Authority we reveal and light up the first 3 of these 7 candidates. What are the first 3 contenders for 2011 Cigar of the Year, and how did they make the cut? There's only one way to find out. See you on the inside!
